OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775113301
OL,3,CStarmer reiterates UK will not be
OL,4,C'dragged' into Iran conflict, despite
OL,5,C'noise'
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer once again emphasised
OL,8,Fon Wednesday that the UK will not be
OL,9,F"dragged into" the war in Iran, saying
OL,10,Fit would not be in the national
OL,11,Finterest to do so.
OL,13,FBut he also warned that the impact of
OL,14,Fthe war in the Middle East will
OL,15,F"affect the future of our country",
OL,16,Fbut emphasised that "no matter how
OL,17,Ffierce this storm, we are well-placed
OL,18,Fto weather it."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
