FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775113301
OL,3,CStarmer reiterates UK will not be
OL,4,C'dragged' into Iran conflict, despite
OL,5,C'noise'
OL,7,FSpeaking during a Downing Street press
OL,8,Fconference, the prime minister also
OL,9,Fsought to dismiss President Trump's
OL,10,Frecent comments on Nato as "noise".
OL,12,FIt comes as US President Donald Trump
OL,13,Fsays he is considering withdrawing the
OL,14,FUS from the bloc, after allies did not
OL,15,Fjoin his war with Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775113301
OL,3,CStarmer reiterates UK will not be
OL,4,C'dragged' into Iran conflict, despite
OL,5,C'noise'
OL,7,FAsked by The Telegraph on Wednesday
OL,8,Fwhether he would reconsider the US's
OL,9,Fmembership in Nato, Trump said: "I was
OL,10,Fnever swayed by Nato. I always knew
OL,11,Fthey were a paper tiger, and Putin
OL,12,Fknows that too, by the way."
OL,14,FTrump also criticised the UK in
OL,15,Fparticular for refusing to get
OL,16,Finvolved in the US-Israeli war against
OL,17,FIran, and suggested the Royal Navy was
OL,18,Fnot ready.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775113301
OL,3,CStarmer reiterates UK will not be
OL,4,C'dragged' into Iran conflict, despite
OL,5,C'noise'
OL,7,FStarmer dismisses "noise" after Trump
OL,8,Fsays he is considering pulling out of
OL,9,FNato
OL,11,FAsked about the US president's
OL,12,Fcomments on Wednesday, Sir Keir said:
OL,13,F"Nato is the single most effective
OL,14,Fmilitary alliance the world has ever
OL,15,Fseen, and it has kept us safe for many
OL,16,Fdecades.
OL,18,F"We are fully committed to Nato.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775113301
OL,3,CStarmer reiterates UK will not be
OL,4,C'dragged' into Iran conflict, despite
OL,5,C'noise'
OL,7,F"Secondly, that whatever the pressure
OL,8,Fon me and others, whatever the noise,
OL,9,FI'm going to act in the British
OL,10,Fnational interest in all the decisions
OL,11,Fthat I make.
OL,13,F"And that's why I've been absolutely
OL,14,Fclear that this is not our war and
OL,15,Fwe're not going to get dragged into
OL,16,Fit."
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
