OL,3,CStarmer reiterates UK will not be
OL,4,C'dragged' into Iran conflict, despite
OL,5,C'noise'
OL,7,FIn an interview published on
OL,8,FWednesday, Trump criticised Nato
OL,9,Fallies for refusing to send warships
OL,10,Fto reopen the Strait of Hormuz, which
OL,11,FTehran has closed for weeks, causing
OL,12,Fgas and oil to spike.
OL,14,FThe US president told The Telegraph:
OL,15,F"Beyond not being there, it was
OL,16,Factually hard to believe. And I didn't
OL,17,Fdo a big sale. I just said, 'Hey', you
OL,18,Fknow, I didn't insist too much. I just
OL,19,Fthink it should be automatic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775113301
OL,3,CStarmer reiterates UK will not be
OL,4,C'dragged' into Iran conflict, despite
OL,5,C'noise'
OL,7,F"We've been there automatically,
OL,8,Fincluding Ukraine. Ukraine wasn't our
OL,9,Fproblem. It was a test, and we were
OL,10,Fthere for them, and we would always
OL,11,Fhave been there for them. They weren't
OL,12,Fthere for us."
OL,14,FMr Trump rebuked the UK in particular
OL,15,Ffor refusing to get involved in the US-
OL,16,FIsraeli war against Iran, and
OL,17,Fsuggested the Royal Navy was not ready.
OL,19,FHe said: "You don't even have a navy.
OL,20,FYou're too old and had aircraft
OL,21,Fcarriers that didn't work."
OL,26,@{D@JOU}D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/27
