OL,3,CStarmer reiterates UK will not be
OL,4,C'dragged' into Iran conflict, despite
OL,5,C'noise'
OL,7,FAsked if the prime minister should
OL,8,Fspend more on defence, Mr Trump said:
OL,9,F"I'm not going to tell him what to do.
OL,10,FHe can do whatever he wants. It
OL,11,Fdoesn't matter. All Starmer wants is
OL,12,Fcostly windmills that are driving your
OL,13,Fenergy prices through the roof."
OL,26,@qD@AOUuD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/27
