OL,3,CStarmer reiterates UK will not be
OL,4,C'dragged' into Iran conflict, despite
OL,5,C'noise'
OL,7,FDuring his speech, Starmer emphasised
OL,8,Fthe need for closeness with Europe,
OL,9,Fand announced that the Foreign
OL,10,FSecretary, Yvette Cooper, will host a
OL,11,Fmeeting with international leaders to
OL,12,F"assess all viable diplomatic and
OL,13,Fpolitical measures" to reopen the
OL,14,FStrait of Hormuz.
OL,16,F35 countries have signed a statement
OL,17,Fcommitting to work together to restore
OL,18,Fmaritime security to the shipping
OL,19,Froute.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
