OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775113301
OL,3,CStarmer reiterates UK will not be
OL,4,C'dragged' into Iran conflict, despite
OL,5,C'noise'
OL,7,FStarmer said "a united front of
OL,8,Fmilitary strength and diplomatic
OL,9,Factivity" is needed to restore
OL,10,Fstability.
OL,12,FTrump says US could be done with the
OL,13,Fwar in coming weeks
OL,15,FTrump said overnight that the US
OL,16,Fmilitary could end its war in Iran in
OL,17,F"two or three weeks" and will shift
OL,18,Fresponsibility for the Strait of
OL,19,FHormuz to countries that rely on it
OL,20,Ffor oil and shipping.
OL,26,@oD@NOUqD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/27
