OL,3,CStarmer reiterates UK will not be
OL,4,C'dragged' into Iran conflict, despite
OL,5,C'noise'
OL,7,FSpeaking from the Oval Office, the
OL,8,Fpresident said: "We have had regime
OL,9,Fchange. Now, regime change was not one
OL,10,Fof the things I had as a goal. I had
OL,11,Fone goal: they will have no nuclear
OL,12,Fweapon, and that goal has been
OL,13,Fattained.
OL,15,F"They will not have nuclear weapons.
OL,16,FBut we're finishing the job, and I
OL,17,Fthink within maybe two weeks, maybe a
OL,18,Fcouple of days longer, to do the job.
OL,19,FBut we want to knock out every single
OL,20,Fthey have."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
