OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775113301
OL,3,CStarmer reiterates UK will not be
OL,4,C'dragged' into Iran conflict, despite
OL,5,C'noise'
OL,7,FIran's clerical and military
OL,8,Festablishment remains in control of
OL,9,Fthe country, with some of the most
OL,10,Fhard-line factions still extant.
OL,11,FTrump, however, continues to insist
OL,12,Fthat regime change has been achieved.
OL,14,FHe added that it's possible the war
OL,15,Fcould end sooner if a deal is reached.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775113301
OL,3,CStarmer reiterates UK will not be
OL,4,C'dragged' into Iran conflict, despite
OL,5,C'noise'
OL,7,F"It's possible that we'll have a deal
OL,8,Fbecause they want to make a deal. They
OL,9,Fwant to make a deal more than I want
OL,10,Fto make a deal. But in a fairly short
OL,11,Fperiod of time, we'll be finished,"
OL,12,FTrump said.
OL,14,FTrump also said that the reopening of
OL,15,Fthe Strait of Hormuz should be the
OL,16,Fproblem of other countries, saying it
OL,17,Fhas nothing to do with the US.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
