CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775113301
OL,3,CStarmer reiterates UK will not be
OL,4,C'dragged' into Iran conflict, despite
OL,5,C'noise'
OL,7,F"If France or some other country wants
OL,8,Fto get oil or gas, you go up through
OL,9,Fthe strait and ` the Hormuz Strait `
OL,10,Fthey'll go right up there and they'll
OL,11,Fbe able to fend for themselves," he
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"What happens in the strait, we're
OL,15,Fgoing to have nothing do with," he
OL,16,Fadded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
