OL,3,CStarmer reiterates UK will not be
OL,4,C'dragged' into Iran conflict, despite
OL,5,C'noise'
OL,7,FThe Strait is a narrow waterway off
OL,8,FIran connecting the Persian Gulf to
OL,9,Fthe open ocean, through which a fifth
OL,10,Fof the world's oil sails on a typical
OL,11,Fday.
OL,13,FThe president appeared to echo his
OL,14,Fearlier comments in which he appeared
OL,15,Fto criticise what he sees as the UK's
OL,16,Flack of action in the region.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
