OL,3,CStarmer reiterates UK will not be
OL,4,C'dragged' into Iran conflict, despite
OL,5,C'noise'
OL,7,FPosting on Truth Social, Trump called
OL,8,Fon the UK to "build up some delayed
OL,9,Fcourage" and "take" the Strait of
OL,10,FHormuz, which has been mostly closed
OL,11,Fsince the conflict began.
OL,13,F"You'll have to start learning how to
OL,14,Ffight for yourself, the U.S.A. won't
OL,15,Fbe there to help you anymore, just
OL,16,Flike you weren't there for us," Trump
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,19,F"Iran has been, essentially,
OL,20,Fdecimated. The hard part is done. Go
OL,21,Fget your own oil!"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
