OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775113301
OL,3,CStarmer reiterates UK will not be
OL,4,C'dragged' into Iran conflict, despite
OL,5,C'noise'
OL,7,FIran says it is prepared for longer
OL,8,Fconflict
OL,10,FMeanwhile, Iran has said it is
OL,11,Fprepared for "at least six months" of
OL,12,Fwar, according to its foreign minister.
OL,14,FSpeaking to Al Jazeera, Abbas Araghchi
OL,15,Fsaid: "We do not set any deadlines for
OL,16,Fdefending ourselves. We will defend
OL,17,Four country and our people as far as
OL,18,Fnecessary and by any means required."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
