PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775113301
OL,3,CStarmer reiterates UK will not be
OL,4,C'dragged' into Iran conflict, despite
OL,5,C'noise'
OL,7,F"It does not matter what timelines our
OL,8,Fenemies set for themselves. However,
OL,9,Four recommendation is that they bring
OL,10,Fthis war to a complete and permanent
OL,11,Fend before facing further damage," he
OL,12,Fsaid, noting an end to the war must
OL,13,Finclude peace throughout the entire
OL,14,Fregion.
