OL,3,CStarmer reiterates UK will not be
OL,4,C'dragged' into Iran conflict, despite
OL,5,C'noise'
OL,7,FHe added that Tehran is not in direct
OL,8,Fnegotiations with the US despite
OL,9,Fclaims made by the Trump
OL,10,Fadministration.
OL,12,F"Negotiation is when two countries
OL,13,Fengage in talks to reach an agreement,
OL,14,Fand such a thing does not exist
OL,15,Fbetween us and the United States,"
OL,16,FAraghchi said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/27
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
