OL,3,CStarmer reiterates UK will not be
OL,4,C'dragged' into Iran conflict, despite
OL,5,C'noise'
OL,7,FHe did say he has received messages
OL,8,Ffrom US Special Envoy Steve Witkoff,
OL,9,Fand that the US and Iran have
OL,10,Fcommunicated indirectly through
OL,11,Fintermediaries.
OL,13,FHouthi involvement continues
OL,15,FThe Iranian-backed Houthis in Yemen
OL,16,Fsaid Wednesday they fired a barrage of
OL,17,Fballistic missiles toward Israel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/27
