OL,3,CStarmer reiterates UK will not be
OL,4,C'dragged' into Iran conflict, despite
OL,5,C'noise'
OL,7,FAir raid sirens went off in southern
OL,8,FIsrael in the early morning, from
OL,9,FBeersheba to the Mediterranean coast
OL,10,Ffollowing the launch. There were no
OL,11,Fimmediate reports of impacts.
OL,13,FBrig. Gen. Yahya Saree, a military
OL,14,Fspokesman for the Houthis, said in a
OL,15,Fprerecorded statement that they fired
OL,16,Fat "sensitive targets" in southern
OL,17,FIsrael.
OL,19,FThe attack is the third since the
OL,20,FHouthis joined the war on Friday.
