OL,13,FIsrael strikes a factory in Iran,
OL,14,Fclaiming it supplies fentanyl for
OL,15,Fchemical weapons
OL,17,FIsrael said early Wednesday it struck
OL,18,Fa plant which supplies Iran with
OL,19,Ffentanyl, a powerful synthetic opioid,
OL,20,Fto allegedly use in a chemical weapons
OL,21,Fprogramme.
