OL,7,FIran acknowledged the strike on Tofigh
OL,8,FDaru factory, but insisted it only
OL,9,Fsupplied "hospital drugs" used in
OL,10,Fmedical operations.
OL,12,FThe strike happened on Tuesday, both
OL,13,Fthe Israelis and the Iranians said.
OL,15,FIran's foreign minister posted a
OL,16,Fpicture of the factory in Tehran,
OL,17,Fwriting on X: "The war criminals in
OL,18,FIsrael are now openly and unashamedly
OL,19,Fbombing pharmaceutical companies."
