OL,7,FLebanon's Health Ministry has said
OL,8,Fthat at least five people have been
OL,9,Fkilled during an Israeli strike on a
OL,10,Fneighbourhood in Beirut.
OL,12,FThe organisation added that in a
OL,13,Fpreliminary count early on Wednesday,
OL,14,F21 people were also wounded in the
OL,15,Fstrike in Jnah.
OL,17,FThe strike came without warning, and
OL,18,FIsrael did not declare the target.
