OL,11,FIranian drone attack causes fire at
OL,12,FKuwait International Airport
OL,14,FA drone attack by Iran and its allies
OL,15,Fhit a fuel tank at Kuwait
OL,16,FInternational Airport, sparking a
OL,17,Ffire, authorities have said.
OL,19,FThe state-run KUNA news agency said
OL,20,Fthe attack early Wednesday sparked a
OL,21,F"large fire" at the airport.
